:: whet [code] {"position":"1703,698","size":"200,200"}
<div class="text-tt">
Your body relaxes as you cross your legs, nestling your glass [[whetting bottle]] in the crook between ankle and thigh. You've been carrying the bottle for days, storm waiting. The metal is cool against your legs in the heavy air.<br>

It was [[Malv]] who gave you the small and beautifully carved wooden box that holds your whetting bottle, a little while after it all first happened. Thoughtful, you stare out at the water as you mindlessly pass your thumb over it. In your uncle's grandfather's time, which was not particularly unlike the time before, it was believed that drinking water [[tinctured->tincture]] with chlorophyll and algae focused the mind, "sharpened the words." You like to imagine that the grassy flavor is to remind you that you are as much made of land as you are of sea. The oxygen green surface of an indigo vat, the entrance to its deep blue.<br>

You notice that more people have arrived on the beach. Out of courtesy you avert your eyes as others join the gather. Most talkers, like you, have simply taken to almost always wearing [[undergarments that double as perfectly respectable sea clothes ->Seaware]]. But tellings have always been private affairs, even though so much of modern society has arranged itself around making them available to everyone. Friends and family or even co-workers might arrive to the water together but, as they approached the shore, silence would open, and each would head off to their own solitary spot.<br>

You smile, thinking about how difficult it used to be to resist yelling out a greeting to a school-friend, or to tell someone how much you liked the color of their seaware. //[[The quiet, ->mazuko]]// your teacher once said, //is what makes the gather possible//.<br>

<<nobr>>
<<if $tears is 0>>Rain..<</if>>

<<if $tears is 1>>You take a sip of your water, longing for [[empty.->Emptied]]<</if>>

<<if $tears gte 2 and $ocean is 1>><<include "dive">><</if>>

<<if $tears gt 1>>Your face is wet as you stand and [[head for the shoreline->shoreline]]<</if>><</nobr>>
</div>


